<s docid="FBIS4-50830" num="8"> Zhejiang Passes New Laws Against Child Labor</s>
</TI>
</H3>
<HT>
<F>
<PHRASE>

<s docid="FBIS4-50830" num="9"> Zhejiang Passes New Laws Against Child Labor</s>
</PHRASE>
</F>
</HT>
<F>

<s docid="FBIS4-50830" num="10"> HK2305093894 Hong Kong EASTERN EXPRESS in English 23 May 94 p 9</s>
</F>
<F>

<s docid="FBIS4-50830" num="11"> HK2305093894</s>
</F>
