<H3>
<TI>

<s docid="FBIS3-20336" num="7"> Employers, Trade Minister Advocate Social Clause</s>
</TI>
</H3>
<F>

<s docid="FBIS3-20336" num="8"> BR2903140094 Paris LA TRIBUNE DESFOSSES in French 29 Mar 94 p 5</s>
</F>
<F>

<s docid="FBIS3-20336" num="9"> BR2903140094</s>
